summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of coach dashboard application. All major features working perfectly including dashboard home, videos management, challenges management, CRUD operations, navigation, and design system compliance. Mock API integration working correctly.

design_issues.issue: Challenge status shows 'Ended' instead of 'Active' due to mock data dates being in the past

passed_tests: Dashboard home page loads with stats cards showing correct API data (3 videos, 2 challenges, 156 members, 12 live classes)
Dashboard quick actions buttons (Upload Video, Create Challenge, Schedule Live Class) are clickable and navigate correctly
Recent Videos and Recent Challenges sections load and display mock API data properly
Sidebar navigation works correctly between Dashboard, Videos, and Challenges pages
Videos page displays list of videos with search functionality working
Videos page Upload Video button navigates to create form correctly
Videos page Edit buttons navigate to edit pages correctly
Videos page Delete buttons open confirmation modals with proper content and Cancel/Delete options
Create Video form displays all required fields (title, description, duration, category, target area)
Create Video form validation prevents submission of empty form (title required)
Create Video form submission works correctly and redirects to videos page
Create Video form target area selection buttons work properly
Create Video form file upload areas present for video and thumbnail
Create Video form publish checkbox functionality works
Challenges page displays list of challenges with search functionality working
Challenges page Create Challenge button navigates to create form correctly
Challenges page Edit buttons navigate to edit pages correctly
Challenges page Delete buttons open confirmation modals with proper content
Create Challenge form displays all required fields (title, description, dates, type, visibility)
Create Challenge form validation prevents submission of empty form (title and dates required)
Create Challenge form submission works correctly and redirects to challenges page
Create Challenge form challenge type selection buttons work properly
Create Challenge form visibility radio buttons work correctly
Create Challenge form cover image upload area present
Toast notification system working correctly on form submissions
Design system compliance: Primary color #308FAB properly used throughout
Design system compliance: Poppins font properly loaded and applied
Responsive grid layouts working correctly for stats cards and content
Fixed sidebar layout with proper main content positioning (ml-64)
Interactive elements have proper hover and focus states
All CRUD operations working through mock API endpoints
Navigation between all pages works seamlessly via sidebar and buttons
Form back navigation works correctly on all create/edit pages
Search functionality works on both Videos and Challenges pages
Modal dialogs (delete confirmations) work properly with proper content and actions
